These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-7-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, filmmaking, baking, photography
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, havana, alhambra, blend
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, lavender, ivory, grey
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, june, december
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, daisy, orchid, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, handball, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, subway, tram
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 2. the person who likes lavender is the person who growsazalea##1
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is not the person driving the car##6
 4. the person driving the subway is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
 6. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
 7. the person driving the tram is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the alhambra-smoker is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
10. the blend-smoker is the person driving the car##1
11. the alhambra-smoker is the person driving the boat##1
12. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
14. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
15. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
16. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the tram##7
17. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
18. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
19. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the bongani-smoker and the person who's sport is baseball##7
20. the person who growsdaisy is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
21. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby          | magic-tricks      | photography   | filmmaking     | baking |
| Cigar           | blend | havana   | bongani    | alhambra     |
| Color   | grey       | ivory | apricot   | lavender   |
